---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <div class="text-sm font-light">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Enes, an AI & Software Engineer from Turkey.
        <br />
        My primary tools of choice include:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Python (FastAPI, PyTorch, Langchain)</li>
        <li>React & Next.js</li>
        <li>Node.js (NestJS, Express)</li>
        <li>C++ & C# (OpenCV, Unity)</li>
        <li>Firebase & Cloud (AWS, GCP, Azure)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Beyond coding, I have a deep passion for building startups, experimenting with Generative AI, and autonomous systems. I recently founded Destek Chat, an AI customer service platform.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      I believe in choosing the right tool for the job. Whether it's training custom RLHF models or shipping a mobile app, I focus on building robust, performant, and scalable solutions.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
